inners/ |title=San Diego Film Critics Society\u2019s 2016 Award Winners |date=December 12, 2016 |accessdate=December 12, 2016}}</ref>\n| [[San Diego Film Critics Society Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n| ''The Handmaiden''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| [[San Francisco Film Critics Circle Awards 2016|San Francisco Film Critics Circle]]<ref name=\"SFrancisco\">{{cite web|url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/2016/12/09/san-francisco-film-critics-circle-nominations/ |title=San Francisco Film Critics Circle Nominations! |first=Marshall |last=Flores |publisher=AwardsDaily.com |date=December 9, 2016 |accessdate=December 10, 2016}}</ref><ref name=\"SFFCC2016\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/moonlight-named-best-picture-by-san-francisco-film-critics-circle-955302 |title='Moonlight' Named Best Picture by San Francisco Film Critics Circle |first=Kimberly |last=Nordyke |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=December 12, 2016 |accessdate=December 12, 2016}}</ref>\n| [[San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]]\n| Park Chan-wook and Chung Seo-kyung\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| [[San Francisco Film Critics Circle Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n| ''The Handmaiden''\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Production Design\n| Ryu Seong-hee\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association Awards 2016|St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stlfilmcritics.org/awards |title=2016 StLFCA Annual Award Nominations |publisher=[[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association]] |date=December 12, 2016 |accessdate=December 12, 2016}}</ref>\n| Best Production Design\n| Ryu Seong-hee\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| Best Foreign Language Film\n| ''The Handmaiden''\n| {{draw|Runner-up}}\n|-\n| [[Toronto Film Critics Association Awards 2016|Toronto Film Critics Association]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/moonlight-